Class BukkitInformationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.com.djrapitops.plan.systems.info.InformationManager
      • main.java.com.djrapitops.plan.systems.info.BukkitInformationManager

  • public class BukkitInformationManager
extends InformationManager
    Manages the Information going to the PageCache.

    This means Inspect and Analysis pages as well as managing what is sent to Bungee WebServer when one is in use.
